      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんの様子がずっとおかしかった理由が\n分かって安心しましたよ",
      "startTime": 114.722630985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズに挑むのが琴乃ちゃんだけ\n初めてだったから、ずっと緊張してたみたいです",
      "startTime": 119.322630985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも……{user}さんも\nなかなかでしたよ？",
      "startTime": 125.8559622838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　なかなかって……何が？",
      "startTime": 127.6892956172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "私が琴乃ちゃんを心配してる時\nずーっと様子がおかしかったじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 133.7476628536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はは……バレないで済んだだけ良しとしてくれ",
      "startTime": 136.7476628536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、怪しまれてもみんなバレないように振る舞って\nそこまで頑張って準備してくれたのが嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 144.9995449934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロに入って……月ストの一員になれて\n本当に良かったって、改めて思えました",
      "startTime": 152.6995490623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "渚……そう言ってもらえると俺も嬉しいよ",
      "startTime": 156.166215729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
